    <text>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_16b8738b">
            <lb />Welte-Mignon
         </div>
         <div facs="#eSc_textblock_1f92a58e">
            <lb />
                <hi rendition="#c">
                    <seg ana="#virtual_presence" type="topic" resp="#np">
                        THE MASTER'S FINGERS ON YOUR PIANO
                    </seg>
                </hi>
         </div>

         <div facs="#eSc_textblock_f12fe344" type="illustration">
            <seg ana="#listening" resp="#np" type="topic">
                <figure>
                    <desc>
                        Painting of Pachmann sitting at a piano. Three men in the background observing him.
                    </desc>
                </figure>
            </seg>
        </div>

        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_be99ecd4">
            <lb />
            <seg ana="#immortality" resp="#np" type="topic">
                <hi rendition="#i">Through You I Live Forever</hi>
            </seg>
         </div>
         <div facs="#eSc_textblock_c488bbeb">
            <quote>
                <lb />"BRAVO! BRAVO! Welte Mignon*! You have
                <lb />given me one of the greatest
                experiences of my
                <lb />life. You have made my fondest dream come true-
                <lb />the dream of a perfect recording method and a re-
                <lb />producing mechanism
                <seg ana="#immortality">
                    thru which my playing as
                    an
                    <lb />interpretative artist might live forever.
                </seg>
                You are my
                <lb />undying 'alter ego'–thru you my own invisible hands
                <lb />render the spell of my Chopin, my Liszt. You have
                <lb />my unqualified endorsement.
                <seg ana="#immortality">
                    <hi rendition="#i">Thru you I live forever."</hi>
                </seg>
            </quote>
         </div>
         <div facs="#eSc_textblock_6aa6819d">
            <lb />
            <signed>
                <persName corresp="https://d-nb.info/gnd/116014490">V. de Pachmann</persName>
            </signed>
         </div>
         <div facs="#eSc_textblock_5b251767">
            <hi rendition="#i">
                <lb />A letter from the great
                <lb />
                <persName corresp="https://d-nb.info/gnd/116014490">Vladimir de Pachmann</persName>,
                the idol of
                <lb />his time, the most celebrated
                <lb />pianist of a century; rejuve-
                <lb />nated at 75, and now playing
                <lb />as no one ever played before."
            </hi>
         </div>
         <div facs="#eSc_textblock_e4393655">
            <lb />Installed invisibly in any piano,
            <seg ana="#exact_reproduction" resp="#np" type="topic">
                Welte-Mignon* Reproducing Action makes that
                <lb />piano reproduce with absolute perfection the playing of the master pianists.
            </seg> The
            <lb />Library contains thousands of beautiful recordings. You can choose from 112
            <lb />standard makes of pianos that now install the Welte-Mignon* Reproducing Action.
            <lb />Send for the beautiful art brochure
         </div>
         <div facs="#eSc_textblock_9d2e8e27">
            <hi rendition="#c">
                <lb /><orgName key="auto.pneumatic.action">The AUTO PNEUMATIC ACTION CO.</orgName>,
                653 West 51st Street, New York
                <lb /><persName>WILLIAM C. HEATON</persName>, President
                <lb />*Licensed under original <orgName>Welte Mignon</orgName> patents
            </hi>
         </div>
